{"word":"G630 - ἀπολύω - apolýō - ap-ol-oo'-o - Depart","slug":"G630","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπολύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apolýō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ol-oo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Depart"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - apoluo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ap-ol-oo'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>free</i> fully, that is, (literally) <i>relieve</i>, <i>release</i>, <i>dismiss</i> (reflexively <i>depart</i>), or (figuratively) <i>let die</i>, <i>pardon</i>, or (specifically) <i>divorce:</i> - (let) depart, dismiss, divorce, forgive, let go, loose, put (send) away, release, set at liberty."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629\">G629</a>"}]}